tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hbl1665703121181.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hbl1665703121181.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hbl1665703121181.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hbl1665703121181\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Return Method\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Location of values returned by non-Uniface operations at run time. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">In $status</code> (default; mandatory for Uniface components and service stored procedures), or <code class=\"ph codeph\">In first parameter</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__section_w2219ab1b5b1_w2220ab1b5_w2221ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Returned values are discarded (cast to void), unless there are errors. This is the default value for Java implementations.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">In $status</code> (default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the value of the function to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>. Select a data type for the return value from the drop-down list. The default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Long</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Mandatory value for Uniface components and service stored procedures.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">In first parameter</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hbl1665703121181__table_d13016e1_d13017e1_d13018e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return value in the first parameter of the operation. If the operation does not have a first parameter defined as Out, you are warned that it is not possible to specify a return value in the first parameter.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__section_jhh_hsp_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297973e157\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__ul_jvd_3sp_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hbl1665703121181__li_d3113e1_d3114e1_d3115e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ird1665702714456.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ird1665702714456.html\" title=\"A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.\">Signature</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613436\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613436\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Return Method Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return Method Location of values returned by non-Uniface operations at run time. Valid values are None , In $status (default; mandatory for Uniface components and service stored procedures), or In first parameter . Value Description None Returned values are discarded (cast to void), unless there are errors. This is the default value for Java implementations. In $status (default) Return the value of the function to $status . Select a data type for the return value from the drop-down list. The default is Long . Mandatory value for Uniface components and service stored procedures. In first parameter Return value in the first parameter of the operation. If the operation does not have a first parameter defined as Out, you are warned that it is not possible to specify a return value in the first parameter. Applies To Signature Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}